<refsect1 role="desc">
<title role="desc.title">Description</title>
<para>
SexyUrlLabel is a GtkLabel with support for embedded hyperlinks. It uses a
modified form of the Pango markup format that supports the
&lt;a href="..."&gt;...&lt;/a&gt; tag. The hyperlink will appear in blue and
can be activated by clicking it. Right-clicking the hyperlink displays a menu
offering the ability to activate it or to copy the URL.
</para>
</refsect1>

